data.title: Thailand's Crown Prince and Princess are divorcing after 13 years of marriage
data.meta_description: Another royal couple has decided to split — Thailand’s Crown Prince Vajiralongkorn and wife Princess Srirasmi Akrapongpreecha are getting a divorce after 13 years of marriage.
